[31/07/2018 23:05:40] <font color="#ffff00">Sí... Te llaman a ti.</font>
[31/07/2018 23:05:42] <font color="#ffffff">-¡Bill Carson!</font>
[31/07/2018 23:05:52] <font color="#00ffff">Sí... Soy... Bill Carson.</font>
[31/07/2018 23:05:54] <font color="#ffffff">-Mira, Bill Carson.</font>
[31/07/2018 23:05:57] <font color="#ffffff">Aquí... se contesta: "presente".</font>
