[31/07/2018 23:06:06] <font color="#00ffff">¡Ay!</font>
[31/07/2018 23:06:10] <font color="#ffffff">-Responde: "presente".</font>
[31/07/2018 23:06:13] <font color="#00ffff">Los tíos gordos</font>
