[31/07/2018 23:09:57] <font color="#00ff00">Adelante.</font>
[31/07/2018 23:10:01] <font color="#00ff00">Pasa ya, Tuco.</font>
[31/07/2018 23:10:04] <font color="#00ff00">No gastes cumplidos.</font>
