[31/07/2018 23:11:30] <font color="#00ffff">Ajá.</font>
[31/07/2018 23:11:30] <font color="#00ff00">Ajá.</font>
[31/07/2018 23:11:34] <font color="#00ff00">Entonces si estabas con</font>
